{"type":null,"faqId":10323,"title":"秘盒M310  CNTV节目点播","answer":"<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<a name=\"_Toc372020426\"></a><span>1.1.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">怎么选择节目与收藏节目？</span><span></span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方法一：在节目的播放介绍界面，点击</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">收藏</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">可以将节目添加到</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">收藏</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">里，如下收藏图示：</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31201\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方法二：在节目详情页按遥控器上</span><span>“</span><span>☆</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">键也可收藏节目</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">影视</span><span>”—&gt;“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">更多影视</span><span>”—&gt;“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我的收藏</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中找到已收藏节目</span> \n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<a name=\"_Toc372020427\"></a><span>1.1.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">如何选择高清标清？</span><span></span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在点击</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">播放</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后，会出现提示：选择</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">高清</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">还是</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">标清</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。请根据家中的实际网络带宽与流畅度来选择，以免影响观看体验</span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31202\" alt=\"\" /> \n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<a name=\"_Toc372020428\"></a><span>1.1.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">节目暂停、快进退、声音调节？</span><span></span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">节目暂停，请按遥控器上的</span><span>“OK”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">键暂停，再按</span><span>“OK”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">键可恢复播放</span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31203\" alt=\"\" /> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">节目快进，请长按遥控器上的</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">向右</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">键</span> <span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31205\" width=\"30\" height=\"25\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">；节目快退，请长按</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">向左</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方向键</span><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31206\" width=\"27\" height=\"24\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">快进的速度视节目长度而定</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">声音调节，请按</span><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31207\" width=\"99\" height=\"32\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进行音量增减，屏幕显示音量大小</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31208\" width=\"265\" height=\"53\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span> </span>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<a name=\"_Toc372020429\"></a><span>1.1.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">节目搜索怎么使用？</span><span></span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">搜索</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">界面输入节目首字母，可搜索到想观看的节目</span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31209\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<a name=\"_Toc372020430\"></a><span>1.1.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">播放记录会清空吗？可以手动清空吗？</span><span></span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span s